{{基督教末世论}}

'''时代论'''（{{lang-en|Dispensationalism}}），又称'''时代主义'''，是一种[[基督教末世論|終末論]]、未來主義、[[釋經學|釋經學]]理論，相信神在《[[聖經|聖經]]》聖約中透過一系列的「時代（dispensations）」，或歷史上的時期，以不同方式而完成給與人類的啟示，屬於[[千禧年前论|千禧年前论]]的一种形式，活跃于许多保守派[[基督新教|基督新教]]信徒和其他保守派基督徒团体中。“Dispensation”一词相信來自[[英王|英王]][[钦定版圣经|钦定版《圣经》英文译本]]的《[[以弗所书|以弗所书]]》第3章第2-4节<ref>{{cite web| title =以弗所书 3:2-4 (钦定版)| publisher =BibleGateway.com| url =http://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Ephesians%203:2-4;&version=9;| accessdate =2007-11-30}}</ref>，不過亦有反對者認為此用法與其希腊文原文{{lang|el|οỉκονομία}}在《聖經》中的意義不同。

作為一個系統，時代論於[[約翰·納爾遜·達秘|約翰·納爾遜·達秘]]（1800年至1882年）的著作和[[普利茅斯弟兄會|弟兄運動]]中完整闡述<ref name='blaising'>{{Cite book | last1 = Blaising | first1 = Craig A. | first2 = Darrell L | last2 = Bock | title = Progressive Dispensationalism | location = Wheaton, IL | year = 1993 | publisher = BridgePoint | isbn = 1-56476-138-X}}</ref>，再透過《[[司可福串注聖經|司可福串注聖經]]》等作品傳播。時代論的神學由一個獨特的末世觀組成，所有的時代論者堅持[[千禧年前論|千禧年前論]]，大部分堅持信徒災前被提。時代論者認為以色列國家不同於教會，神還沒有實現祂對以色列民族的應許。這些應許包括應許的土地，世界的未來將有千年王國、第三聖殿，在那裡基督再臨，由耶路撒冷<ref>{{Cite book | last = Ryrie | first = Charles Caldwell | title = Basic Theology | url = https://archive.org/details/basictheology0000ryri | location = Wheaton, Ill | publisher = Victor Books | isbn = 0-89693-814-X | year = 1986 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/basictheology0000ryri/page/508 508]–9}}.</ref>統治全世界一千年。在神學其他領域，時代論者堅持福音派和基要派光譜內的立場。<ref name='blaising'/>

隨著時代論的興起，一些新教徒的時代論觀點特別突出，認為《[[啟示錄|啟示錄]]》的內容並不是指過去事件（歷史主義，如[[末世預言實現論|末世預言實現論]]對耶路撒冷在公元70年毀滅的觀點），而是對未來的預測（未來主義）。<ref>{{Citation | first = Gerhard | last = Hasel | title = Crossroads in Prophetic Interpretation: Historicism versus Futurism | type = paper | publisher = World Ministers Council | date = July 3, 1990 | place = Indianapolis, [[Indiana|IN]]}}.</ref><ref>{{Citation | first = Francis Nigel | last = Lee | author-link = Francis Nigel Lee | title = John's Revelation Unveiled | year = 2000}}.</ref><ref>{{Citation | first = David Pio | last = Gullon | title = Two Hundred Years From Lacunza: The Impact of His Eschatalogical Thought on Prophetic Studies and Modern Futurism | publisher = The First International Jerusalem Bible Conference |date=June 1998}}.</ref>依據不同的估計，時代論者在美國的人數就有500萬〜4000萬左右。<ref>[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=huMlsCYyI5YC&pg=PT29 A Case for Historic Premillennialism, edited by Craig L. Blomberg, Sung Wook Chung] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=huMlsCYyI5YC&pg=PT29 |date=20190306044501 }}, p28, estimates 18-25 million in the United States</ref><ref>[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=Fi8sJ6iOX_cC&pg=PA188 Evangelicals and Israel : The Story of American Christian Zionism, By Stephen Spector Professor of English Stony Brook University] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=Fi8sJ6iOX_cC&pg=PA188 |date=20190306044743 }}, p188, estimates 5 million "hard core" dispensationalists in the United States</ref><ref>[http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=dxCREXd3YKIC&pg=PA515 The Oxford Handbook of Millennialism, edited by Catherine Wessinger] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=dxCREXd3YKIC&pg=PA515 |date=20190306043644 }}, p515, estimates as much as 40 million depending on criteria</ref>

